data.description: Assumable VA Loan @ 2.99% Welcome to Hidden Cove, a waterfront community ideally positioned just a short 5-minute drive from Eglin AFB. This home boasts a host of new features including flooring, roof, AC, and a water heater, ensuring comfort and peace of mind.As you enter you are greeted by a massive living space off the kitchen complete with breakfast bar. The upper level has two large bedrooms and two full baths. The master bedroom is a true haven, complete with its own covered deck, offering a private sanctuary to unwind and soak in the surroundings.Nestled along the bayou, this complex provides a backdrop for relaxation after a busy day. Residents have access to the pool and community room, perfect for gatherings. Don't miss the opportunity. Schedule a showing today!
